io.github.thebusybiscuit.slimefun4.core

Class MultiBlock

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.thebusybiscuit.slimefun4.core.MultiBlock

  • public class MultiBlock
extends java.lang.Object
    A MultiBlock represents a structure build in a World. A MultiBlock is often linked to a MultiBlockMachine and is used to recognize that machine in a MultiBlockInteractEvent.
    Author:
    TheBusyBiscuit, Liruxo
    See Also:
    MultiBlockMachine, MultiBlockInteractionHandler, MultiBlockInteractEvent
